00:01:54.379 --> 00:01:55.780
I have to obey him.

00:01:56.340 --> 00:01:58.459
(What leverage could
Cheng Nuo have over her)

00:01:59.159 --> 00:02:01.459
(that would make me
fully trust this materialistic woman?)

00:02:03.459 --> 00:02:04.700
