00:02:06.980 --> 00:02:08.620
poses a deadly threat to you.

00:02:08.939 --> 00:02:10.860
I was coerced by Mu Feng.

00:02:12.419 --> 00:02:13.620
But you did it.

00:02:13.699 --> 00:02:15.780
Now, you must pay the price.

00:02:16.219 --> 00:02:17.419
